differentiate our app from, let's say,

00:01:08.078 --> 00:01:08.908
a dog kennel.

00:01:08.908 --> 00:01:11.703
So we decided to focus
on a niche market.

00:01:11.703 --> 00:01:16.290
And go the same idea, but only for
fancy dogs with the most refined tastes.

00:01:16.290 --> 00:01:18.520
We're going to offer high end services.

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:22.720
We'll only accept sitters who have
nice homes and nice backyards.

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:26.054
Those sitters must take the dogs
on multiple walks a day.

00:01:26.054 --> 00:01:30.175
